        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，飞天老鼠华云龙，在这凤凰岭上落草为寇，倒也逍遥快乐。只因此地有一"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大户人家，他家中有祖传下珍珠凤冠一顶，是我前夜去至他家欲盗此冠，不料"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他家中高挂红灯，照得如同白昼，不能下手。是我空手而回，好不烦闷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，伺候了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启寨主：山下来了许多车辆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "云飞、韩秀，二位贤弟，适才报道，山下来了许多车辆，二位贤弟，下山劫掠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "云飞、韩秀",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "云飞、韩秀",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉了大哥命，只怕不能行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掩门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "华云龙→报子",
          "turns": 1
        },
        {
          "edge": "报子→华云龙",
          "turns": 1
