    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "云飞",
        "华云龙",
        "王通",
        "韩秀"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、华云龙同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "云、韩下山林，未见转回程。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（云飞、韩秀同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "云飞、韩秀",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见大哥。山下来了一大汉，武艺高强，把我们揍回来啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一同前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手、王通同上，同比粗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我道是谁，原来是王大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是华贤弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "华寨主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我同到山寨一叙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正要过山拜望。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众好汉，车辆打至店内，某家去去就来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手同下，华云龙拉王通同下，众人同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "未知大哥驾到，未曾远迎，当面恕罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "备得有酒，与大哥痛饮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到此就要叨扰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，排宴看酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。华云龙、王通同饮酒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王通有一言，不知当讲不当讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥有何金言，当面请讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王通不才，今日在这凤凰岭上，意欲与华贤弟，各位英雄结为金兰之好，每人"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "各戴鲜花一朵，戴花不许采花，如若采花，日后死在众人乱刀之下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这，小弟遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看香案伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同拜，各插花。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "华贤弟，请来戴花。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "花来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愚兄有事在身，不能久留，等某将车辆镖银交纳，再来过山探望。告辞了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "辞别了贤弟下山林，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "插花的事儿要紧记在心。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王通下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "弟兄山寨来结拜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "好似一母共同胎。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（华云龙下，众人同随下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
