    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "云飞",
        "华云龙",
        "韩秀"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（华云龙、云飞、韩秀同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自从与王通来结拜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "每日里闷恹恹愁眉不开。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "云飞、韩秀",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说大哥，这几天愁眉不展，不知为了何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位贤弟有所不知，只因与王通结拜，他道戴花不许采花，故而闷闷不乐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "云飞、韩秀",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "话虽如此，要是真有好花，仍然还是得乐且乐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倘若被王通知晓，俱有不便。"
        },
        {
          "character": "云飞、韩秀",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如今拜把子就是那么一回事，大哥你也太认真啦。待我二人下山打探，如有绝"
        },
        {
          "character": "云飞、韩秀",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "色的女子，我来与大哥送信。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里相见？"
        },
        {
          "character": "云飞、韩秀",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "钟楼相见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，要小心了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
