    {
      "scene_index": 7,
      "label": "第七场",
      "characters_present": [
        "济颠",
        "王通",
        "陈亮",
        "雷鸣"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（济颠上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "济颠",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不念经来不拜忏，终日狗肉蘸烂蒜。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王通、雷鸣、陈亮同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通、雷鸣、陈亮",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见师傅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "济颠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们都来啦，好好，坐下坐下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "济颠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说王通，你的镖车全交清了嘛？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俱已交出。"
        },
        {
          "character": "济颠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你怎么这些日子才回来，道上没有什么劫路的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一路之上，倒也平安。只是路过凤凰岭，遇见华云龙，弟子与他留连几日。"
        },
        {
          "character": "济颠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那小子是个酒色之徒，你理他作什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "弟子曾与他结为金兰，每人各戴鲜花一朵，戴花不许采花如若采花，日后死在"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乱刀之下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "济颠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只管这么说，狗还能改了吃屎么？哎呀！不好，今日晚上，华云龙就要到赵家"
        },
        {
          "character": "济颠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去采花。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，待弟子前去会他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "济颠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢着，慢着。看你们这三个人的脸上，全带着晦气，恐怕都要有灾，待师傅同"
        },
        {
          "character": "济颠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们一齐前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
