      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（济颠上，跑圆场，下。王通、雷鸣、陈亮、华云龙、云飞、韩秀同上，会面。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我道是谁，原来是华贤弟。到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今有雷鸣、陈亮前来赵家楼采花，被小弟看见，特来拿获。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一派胡言。你今采花你可记得插花之事乎？"
        },
        {
          "character": "华云龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了！慢说我无采花，我就是采花，你敢把俺怎么样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你休得逞强。看刀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同起打。华云龙持镖打王通、雷鸣、陈亮，同倒。济颠上，挡华云龙，同下。）"
        }
